{/* CHALLENGES SECTION                                                  */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <!-- Overview -->
  <p class="mb-4">
    Lark Funding offers four distinct funding models: <strong>Instant Funding</strong>, <strong>One Step Challenge</strong>, <strong>Two Step Challenge</strong>, and <strong>Three Step Challenge</strong>. Each model caters to traders with different preferences and risk tolerances, from those seeking immediate funding to those who prefer structured multi-phase evaluations.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-6">
    All challenge types offer an <strong>80% profit split</strong> by default, with the option to upgrade to <strong>90%</strong> by paying an additional 20% of the challenge fee. Account sizes range from <strong>$5,000 to $200,000</strong> (up to $100,000 for Instant Funding), with fees starting from <strong>$60</strong> and going up to <strong>$4,500</strong>.
  </p>

  <!-- Per-challenge summaries -->
