      <p>Account sizes from $5,000 to $100,000 with fees from $200 to $4,500. No evaluation required — start trading and earning immediately. 5% trailing drawdown, 5% daily drawdown, 80% profit split (90% with add-on). First payout on demand, then every 30 days.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">Ideal for experienced traders ready to trade profitably from day one</p>
